FloorUnit - Class in model.staticUnit
The FloorUnit class creates floor units to be used for the world.
A floor unit is a unit shaped like a square that is treated as a floor replace by imageview which has the same image as wall,
with collision on the top, left, and right sides.
The floor collides with any kind of dynamic object.
When an enemy is bubbled, the enemy will still be stopped by a floor unit above it.

Fruit - Class in model.fruit
The Fruit class handles how the fruit is created and interacts with the hero.
The normal fruit is created after a bubble containing an enemy is popped.
The other three are the power up fruit which will show only one of the three in each level.
Four types of fruits one normal fruit, one bubble fruit, one invincible fruit,and one life fruit.
It's a dynamic object.
